<br />\n都唔知邊個無法治精神"},{"pid":"82b365dbf63a67886e75ded8b0d074329e84680a","tid":203541,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港都好似有條咩，係街唔可以漫無目的咁行</blockquote><br />\n遊蕩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有「不誠實使用電腦罪」</blockquote><br />\n哩條成日畀人屌係啲人唔清楚而家啲gadget例如smartphone已經唔再係以前啲只能打出打入嘅手機 已經係一部電腦<br />\n<br />\n電腦有嘅嘢 cpu ram motherboard gpu 都可以喺而家啲手機上面搵到 甚至玩開mod嗰班都喺唔少android機上面裝過windows落去<br />\n<br />\n或者條罪個名係不合時宜嘅 但大眾啲思想更跟唔上時代<br />\n<br />\nsmartphone都面世咗咁多年重以為佢係電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉多個例 ipad叫平板電腦 咁iphone用一樣嘅軟硬件就唔係電腦？<br />\n<br />\n根本好多時連登仔話條罪定義不清其實係源於佢哋本身都唔知咩係電腦 咩唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你定義下咩係電腦</blockquote><br />\n我定義就無意思 連登仔唔會服 不如睇吓oxford dictionary點定義<br />\n<br />\nAn electronic device which is capable of receiving information (data) in a particular form and of performing a sequence of operations in accordance with a predetermined but variable set of procedural instructions (program) to produce a result in the form of information or signals."},{"pid":"3e1d5c88d4511f751f5e70a331d6a3f6661ccff7","tid":203541,"uid":92072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"有條法例係 係條街唱歌走音係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b0cab471f65814a8e93b028c1a91bfe091c113","tid":203541,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港都好似有條咩，係街唔可以漫無目的咁行</blockquote><br />\n遊蕩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有「不誠實使用電腦罪」</blockquote><br />\n哩條成日畀人屌係啲人唔清楚而家啲gadget例如smartphone已經唔再係以前啲只能打出打入嘅手機 已經係一部電腦<br />\n<br />\n電腦有嘅嘢 cpu ram motherboard gpu 都可以喺而家啲手機上面搵到 甚至玩開mod嗰班都喺唔少android機上面裝過windows落去<br />\n<br />\n或者條罪個名係不合時宜嘅 但大眾啲思想更跟唔上時代<br />\n<br />\nsmartphone都面世咗咁多年重以為佢係電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉多個例 ipad叫平板電腦 咁iphone用一樣嘅軟硬件就唔係電腦？<br />\n<br />\n根本好多時連登仔話條罪定義不清其實係源於佢哋本身都唔知咩係電腦 咩唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如你定義下咩係電腦</blockquote><br />\n我定義就無意思 連登仔唔會服 不如睇吓oxford dictionary點定義<br />\n<br />\nAn electronic device which is capable of receiving information (data) in a particular form and of performing a sequence of operations in accordance with a predetermined but variable set of procedural instructions (program) to produce a result in the form of information or signals.</blockquote><br />\n其實你打咁大篇野想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f920eb148e257e22f192361fcefac183f1e62a","tid":203541,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有條法例係 係條街唱歌走音係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港旺角州都需要立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997955edd986b08110829221f923b2af0d54c001","tid":203541,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似有個無海嘅內陸洲有條法例唔比捉鯨魚</blockquote><br />\n條片有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港都有 國際約定問題"},{"pid":"72a4b47f1880a5b1cc013e590284fa145774ca1b","tid":203541,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>德州如果判你有精神病 ,<br />\n可以判死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衣家周街痴線佬<img src=\"/assets